well to give u the short version..i hate being single b/c of how gay guys r!! n if they rnt then their taken!! grr!! well yea n i love working at mOe's..its awesome! n i love kristin...ricky..n i miss n love moriah!!
<3333

well last nite was awesome b/c bekah spent the nite n we stayd up til 7 am than slept until 1240 than we went to mOe's for lunch where we ended up helping them w/ dishes n cleaning dining room...we were dressd sooo HOTT n we did on purpose b/c i lov the look on guys faces at my work when they c me in those kinda clothes..lol...but yea we made up a list of all the workrs at mOe's n we did the thing that my last profile was n we had to make up new questions b/c there were 21 workrs...it was crazy!! i lovd it..n we postd it at work today..evryone was looking at it!! but yea so last nite matt told bekah that tyler likes me...but he doesnt want to b/c i'm 17 but she stuck up for me saying its not illegal..lol..yea so i gav up on having a crush on brent b/c i dont want to date him b/c he's got a gf n all...u knw wat i mean...n tyler doesnt hav a gf..OMG bekah gav me his cell # n i calld him n actd lik i didnt knw who's # it was but yea i did....we talkd for 30 minutes....he's soo cute n he lives by himself in atlantic beach n he surfs a lot n he loves chocolate chip cookie dough ice cream but he cant eat a lot of chocolate at once...i think its cute b/c he loves candy (its his weakness) but he cant eat plain chocolate...lol....so yea i got my check yesterday...$$$$256.06!! heck yea!! i'm so happy n i'm only taking $100 outta that to spend on me....i cant wait til i get my toyota tundra!! it'll b awesome...but yea so i'm trying not to get too attachd to tyler so i dont get weirded out or w/e n run away! like i wasnt suppossed to do w/ chris but yea i wasnt feeling that..u knw...w/e tho..i'm not or at least gonna try not to date ne one til school starts b/c starting a relationship in the summer nevr works out..or at least i dont think it would...i just want to get to knw tyler b/c i was thinking last nite a/b y i liked him n i realizd i dont really knw him so i need to get to knw him n i need to work out b/c i'm so chunky!! i hate it but everyone loves it..i dont understand!! well i'm gonna go to bed but i lov yall <3333 jamie lynn

yea so i dont hav a crush on jimmy ne more b/c idk he was too touchy n i felt very umcomfy around him today when i was w/ ricky, ryan, n him....idk i cant explain it but he was in my bubble n i didnt lik that!! well othr than that i had an awesome day hanging out w/ ryan n ricky....ryan has changd soo much n he's soo tall! lol but yea it was fun n we went into spencer's(i hate that store) but it was fun n weird...lol...but yea today was fun n i cant wait til saturday when i hang out w/ ricky n go to this car club...lol...well i'll finish later <3333 jamie lynn

seriously i hate being single b/c guys suck...well not really but i hav a crush on one guy but i dont want to get involvd rite now b/c all that happend in my last relationship n i'm afraid to love again n to open my heart n soul n give evrything into that relationship but than get burnt to a crisp again!! b/c i dont think i could go thru that again but i dont think this guy would do that b/c he's nevr had a gf b4 n i knw him really well n all but idk..n there's these three really cute guys at owkr but the only one that is single is 20 yrs old n i dont really knw them that well so its kinda just a crush..u knw how that goes...i hate this....being single can b sooo complicatd...argh!! lol but today i hung out w/ ricky n we went to st john's town centr n than to chik-fil-a for lunch than to c war of the worlds which was amazing!! i lovd it...i seriously would recomment it to evryone to c....but yea n we saw jimmy sommer (he's the guy i hav a crush on) at publix...he works there...it was fun...but yea n it was soo cute jimmy askd me to do something tonite but i had to work n he told me that i lookd awesome! but i said i'd gaind some weight n he said it lookd good on me....n ur prob thinking wat a jerk but he was being real w/ me n that's wat i lik in a guy. the only thing that sucks w/ jimmy is that he's nevr had a gf b4 so that makes me more experienced than him n idk...i always seem to get the guys who hav nevr had a gf b4 or had one in a long time....wat's w/ me??...lol..but w/e i want to get to knw him bettr n on a different level so i'm thinking a/b dating him or something....he's really sweet n has the best personality....n he makes me laugh n is cute to boot!! lol that rhymd..kristin...lol...but i'm gonna go b/c i'm tired n i'm hanging out w/ ricky n ryan tom....<3333 jamie lynn

i seriously am soooo sad b/c all but one of my best friends r outta town....thankfully ricky is here so we'r hangin out tom but kristin is in Arizona n moriah is going to rhode island n from there i hav no idea! n i really will miss her...i cried foreva last nite a/b it....<tear>....yea n kristin is gone for 2 weeks i think but i'm not sure so yea it sucks~!! but i hav ricky n work so i'll try to work ass much as possible...n now i hav xc tom n i want to go but than again i dont b/c its kinda boring w/o my friends there...i'll just hav to push hardr n get it ovr w/....i'm gonna go n do things so love yall <3333 jamie lynn

yea ok so i knw yall dont care n prob dont want to hear this but i'm SOOOOOOOOOO horny! i dont want to go into details but its been 4 months!! n wat sucks is evryone i knw has a gf so i'm fuckin outta luck!! lol but yea...i just wanna make out w/ someone....yea ok so i'm a horn dawg! but who isnt ..i hope yall dont judge me on this b/c i knw a lot of yall r feeling it rite now too!! <nuggs with elbow> lol well i'm gonna go find something to do....n no not that u perverts!! gosh!!!!! <3333 jamie lynn

yea so i havnt updatd in FOREVA!! but yea my lov life: i dont want it to go newhere b/c i lik being single n i'm not ready for a new bf netime soon...sry chris...i did it again...but i think he understands b/c he hasnt calld in a day or two so that's kool but neways...i work at moes...WELCOME 2 MOES!! yea that's me! lol well yea kristin n johnny r goin back out!! YEA!! (sarcastically) i just hope she knws wat she's gettin into again b/c i knw i'm not the only one sick of it....but hopefully it'll work out n frankie wrote a NICE comment in response to her tellin evryone..i was like WHOA!! but neways...i'm a work-a-holic now n i lov it....but i dont do nething around the house b/c i'm always at work or at xc..which kristin renee nevr comes to!! o n i cant go to aqua joggin tom in case u c this b/c i dont hav a ride but w/e...i hav ALOT to do around the house so yea n i'v been workin on n now workin in this vbs at my grma's church(its baptist n they keep trying to comvert me! AHHH!) but i'v been hangin w/ dc n amber who really cool so its fun...but othr than that my life is borin n i need to work out more!! hahahaha..that's funny..me work out...!! well i lov yall n i'm out! <3333 jamie lynn

so yea kristin's pressuring me to write so i have to..jkjk..lol...so yea yesterday i got a call from moes n i'm gonna go in today to fill out paperwork n mayb work (YES!!) n yea xc startd today n i ran 3 miles n chris told me he likes me!! yea that like made my nite..it was awesome...yea so i'm trying hard not to get too attachd but sometimes u cant help urself..lol well i'll update better later <3333 jamie lynn

yea so i love that song by the steve miller band song...kristin renee u knw wat i'm talking a/b....that song it sooo funny n is so sam too! i lov that name b/c he doesnt look lik a sam either!! lol well i woke up at noon. which is sooo sweet! b/c i havnt slept in that long in like forever! lol yea so today suckd b/c i went to the pool n well mayb it didnt suck but i hung out w/ some old friends..no aquantinces(sp?)...of mine n yea so i hung out w/ them til 930 tonite at the pool even tho the pool closes at 8pm..yea so it kinda suckd n kinda didnt...yea but i dont hav much to say but kristin renee that's a pimp a$$ song n we need to buy him that cd for his birthday..omg we should buy the cd burn just that one song n burn just that one song like 20 times on a cd soo that's the only song..yea can u tell i'm tired.. lol..well i like the idea anyway..we'll talk a/b it...so yea i'm goin to bed b/c omg i just realized i havnt even been up for 12 hours yet! that's crazy! wow i sound really stoned now! lol well i'm gonna go b4 i do anymore damage! lov ya <3333 jamie lynn

yea so today my daddy came back home n i missed him so much n he gav me the BIGGEST hug ever! so that was kool but other than that i cleaned all day n mowd the lawn..yes guys i mowd a lawn!! so many guys hav been like OMG U mwd a lawn..yea guys i'm kool like that n i can mow a lawn!! losers!! lol well yea so i'm talkin to this kid chris n yea so i'v talkd to him b4 n now we'r talkin again (kristin u knw wat im talkin a/b) n yea moriah gets these gut feelings a/b things that r always rite n yea so she said i shouldnt b as quick to run away from him as i have the other guys i dated just recently..that it'll b good or soemthing like that..so i'm really excited!! :) n he calld tonite to ask me to hang out but i couldnt b/c my dad came home n my parents dont let me go out w/ random ppl <or at least random to them> but i kinda wish i could have..well i'm kinda tired, kinda excited but i'm gonna go...o n ps kristin i love u n ur so much better off w/o johnny or any of his drama...i love u to death girl n i'm here just call me if u need me!! <3333 jamie lynn

today was a lot of fun..i helpd my gramma's church pass out flyers for vbs...than i went to chik-fil-a for lunch n went home n changd....than moriah came in pickd me up<she is the one leavin in three weeks> so we'v been hangin out since than....we came back to her house n printd out n addressd grad enouncements...than we went to walmart n ross..where we bought candy for the movie "the sisterhood of the travelin pants"...it was an amazin movie n touchd me on so many different levels it was incredible...it wasnt exactlly lik the book but u knw how hollywood does...but w/e..today i had a smoothie at the tropical smoothie at atlantic beaches n they nevr make really good smoothies..but do u knw who does??....the one at kernan n atlantic!! they mak the best mango magic!! its my favorite...i LOVE mangos!! lol well today i cried a long time w/ moriah b/c i miss my dad n want him to stay w/ us!! i cant tak bein hurt nemore...i said earlier that i up on this ruse to make ppl think that i dont care but OMG do i care!! i wish he just really knew how much....i am the kinda person who loves..like REALLY loves!! w/ all my heart, mind, n body x infiniti x 2!! gosh i havnt said that in forevr....but neways...yea so my bestest best friend in my whole entire life gave me her cross today..she says she has two but it made me cry hardr than i was already was...her, my mommy, my brother, gramma, n my daddy r the only things that i hold in that special place in my heart that is only savd for extra special ppl..yea i love kristin n ricky..yall knw i do but they r family!! there's nothing like family n now i feel like evrything is spirlin downward but than i look at my situation n i could hav it soooo much worse...my parents could REALLY b divorced, moriah wasnt comin back, n i'm all alone...that's my greatest fear in life..to end up alone in love from someone else like that person ur meant to spend the rest of ur life w/ or alone w/o friends, family, or nething to hold on to....yea evn tho moron burnt me i still believe in love n believe that i wasnt really in love w/ him but infatuated w/ him n i made mistakes but i learnd from it n am sooo much strongr for it so in a way i can thank him for the life lesson he taught me n how he showd me wat i dont want in a guy...b/c no doubt he's a great guy but he wasnt for me...n thats all i hav to say in that subject...when i was first writin in this i askd my friend kristin was she wrot in here...i.e. personal stuff n she said well i writ a/b the things i did or when i hav to vent n soo i kinda use this as a way to vent evn tho the whole world can read it...if anyone evr wantd to really get to knw me they would hav to listen to me talk<which i do A LOT of> n i doubt neone would want to sit there that long..lol...or read wat i writ b/c i writ wat comes to my mind n from my heart...well i lov yall!! toodles <3333 jamie lynn

hey guys its me...well last nite i spent the nite @ kristin's n today we woke up, ran, rode bikes, n a lot of stuff...i havnt run in foreva n today was so much fun but would hav been better if it raind...rite kristin..lol...but yea i cant wait for xc to start but i dont knw y..prob b/c all my friends r in xc...yea n something thats been bothrin me is that fact that my mom n grma say i dont care a/b my dad which i do but i act like i dont to hide the feelins i hav a/b thier probs but they think its an act when i tell them that..i dont understand parents @ all b/c they nevr believe us..y not we will nevr knw but w/e...idk n i cant stand tryin to find someone to date but evryone my age just want a gf or bf n all i want to do is date around n i hate tellin ppl no when they get too attachd or try to go in for the kill..b/c its hard to ask someone out so now i tell them straight up i dont want a bf n than we date for a while, they get attachd, then i hav to tel them again n than they nevr call back..i think its gay but that's just me...but yea i dont hav much to say..lol..n its my first real entry for me so hope yall like it
Hey guys its kristin just messing around trying to make jamie a live journal because im bored
